values:
Yey I'm still alive!~ 

Not much new in my life though =/... I'm back in Canada , where I plan to stay >:D  .

Past months have been complete Arashi-world hahahha... nothing new in that. This month has bee  nice though Anime Evolution was last weekend *_________* so awesome~~ i haven't and that much fun in a while xD I was staff as always and boo no cosplay this year Dx I did get a Yukata ( as b-day present) I wore so it was still good :D .. This year I manage to embarrass  myself  hahahah I participated in anime's best dance crew.. yeah.. why.. I blame Rukia-chan ;;>.> lol oh well it was fun nonetheless.. but if that was not enough I went to Anime Idol auditions on an impulse and guess what??? I forgot the lyrics hahahahahahah oh well still it was fun... but no surprise I was not there for any more rounds hahahha but still i enjoyed it xp.. AE was so much fun :D and to top it Monday after was my b-day yatta \(^^)/  so they got me a cake on Sunday at AE and i got another one at home on Monday *__________* so yummy and fun~~

Other than that not much new.. new LJ layout and yes it's Arashi <3 Aiba Masaki ^^.. not my best work but good enough for my lack of photoshop practice =/ 

Anyways byes minna !~ I hope you are doing well!~

Yey I'm still alive~~

Currently alive in Venezuela hahahaha just until sunday...

What can I say?? coming back is nice.. but it feels so different from before.. i might say, even a bit sad... Now that my mom and dad moved to the US and we come to stay in my auntie's house it feels more like i'm a tourist now... hahahah i even got laughed at when i was taking public trasportation =_= by my mom... yeah i look THAT lost here... The saddest part is my dog Lizi ;_; i think she is deaf now....shows no reaction what so ever when ppl call her.... plus she looks weak and even kind of sick... I should have expected it.. she is almost 12 years old.. but she looked fine last year.. now she is even loosing her teeth ;_;  It really worries me :( .. at least Suki still looks fine a bit skinny but sweet as always..

On the bright side my family still looks good.. even on the decaying situation of our country my family still seems to hang on, the young ones growing so fast, the old ones looking the same,, a bit crazier some of them.. but still fine i guess...

Though I'm happy to see my family and eating all the venezuelan food i've been missing out on.. coming here always makes me come to the same sad realization, I can't live here anymore.. -.-

oh well... i think this i'm alive msg is depressing so far hahahahha ^^;;;;;;;

About th rest of my life well in august hopefully i'll be able to apply for rescidency :D, and my current job is ok... my parents have a house in Houston and it's so pretty i wanna visit them there soon :3.. My sis graduated  last friday, the party was fun even when i was weainf very very high heels hahahah :D

Current obssesions not many.. Books: a lof of Meg Cabot ^^;;;; embarasing truth. Best book in a while though was The Hunger Games, I highly recomend it to those that like teen books xD.. and the latest not bad either was the mortal instruments series by Cassandra Clare which i'm currently reading. Tv wise... not much.. other than every Arashi show that comes my way hahahah yup suffering a very high Arashi fever hahahha. Lots of asian dramas as always.. weirdly enough not watching much anime... sad... but i ahve no idea what's good that's new.. only watching Axis Powers Hetalia.. why? cause it's so weird and random... I wonder if Venezuela will ever show up hahahahah I highly doubt it..

I don;t really need to go but i think my ramble is kind of boring kind of pointles by now hahahah

matta ne~~

Hi everyone *waves from Houston's point in the map*

yeah I've left my home town once more.. I'm gonna miss it ;_; .... I'm in Houston my parent's future living place.. visiting bro and family friends .. just a couple of days... It's really hot here .. i got sunburn in one day D:.. it looks ok.. but everything is so far....

I dun  know if I'm retuning to Van T^T.. i really hope so... I love it there... 

Life is weird... and it has been spinning around a bit lately.. i dun know what the future will bring me..  Soon I need to figure it out ... I'm broke...

waaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaahhhhhhhhhhhhh i'm so worried  *hit head* .. I'll explain later why ^^;;;

*runs in circles*

I've been home around 3 weeks already... I like it lots :D most of the time... of course there's times when I don't but it can't be helped =/

Internet situation is decent.. no wireless... waiting for my bro to come back so he can fix it *_____* less than a week yey!! he is having his graduation on sunday.. a Master... sugoi ;;>.>.. hope he can take care of me when  I become a penniless writer lol.. I just hope he doesn't become a penniless musician  D: ..

Mother's day is sunday... mom won't be here =/ .. though I'm sure she will be having fun in her massive shopping in Indianapolis  hahahaI'll go to granma's it'll be fun ^^

hm.. other things lately... living alone with my sis is not easy .. she just wants to do whatever she likes and i have to be the one scolding her.. and I personally hate it but what else can i do if it affects me what she does... =_=;;;.. other than that things are ok... still getting a little sick lately =_= weird.. and awfully annoying ... on the family well everyone is doing fine it seems... as always it's growing .. Turns out I have a 17 years-old cousin we never knew about lol so soap-opera like... but he seems like a pretty cool/nice kid ^^ My dogs.. well Lizi and Suki are the only ones left at home.. >w<..Lizi looks the same.. honestly I wonder if she took some anti-aging potion ;;>.> turning 11 soon and still as annoying and loud as always lol.. Suki.. she is a sweetheart , thus her name, but she is pretty dumb =/.... *how mean*...

I should take some pictures... 

*goes to take a nap*

Dear Santa...

Dear Santa,

This year I've been busy!

Last Monday I gave change to a homeless guy (19 points). In July I gave a kidney (1000 points). Last month I signed my organ donor card (28 points). In May I got in line at the supermarket at the same time as someone else and I didn't yield (-8 points). In June on a flight to LA, I stole the emergency flight information card (-40 points).

Overall, I've been nice (999 points). For Christmas I deserve a pony!

Sincerely,
MoonAngel_1506

Write your letter to Santa! Enter your LJ username:

wow I've been lj-lazy for a long time... even though I do check it almost everyday i never post.. at least i can have the excuse I don't have an interesting life and I don't really have much new to tell.. I've become (or being for a long time) a Himono-onna.. and if you don't know what I mean just google it or check out the jdrama Hotaru no Hikari xp...

so what has being going on with me since France... wah such a long time ago... i can barely think of it as real...well I got a job =O .. yeah ( and i'm there right now... sunday are a bit slow so I actually have time to be idle and post =p).. I'm working in a call center.. hehe.. i make reservations for hotels.. it's a good job =3 well paid.. nice place, nice ( and patient) ppl... heheheh they have to be to deal with me.. I forget a lot of things.. and everytime i have to fax smth I have to make puppy eyes for smone to come to my aid lol.. though i have to work weekends it's not so bad.. just hoping i can make it at least one day for AE.. i had lost all hopes after the schedules were posted but one of my sup told me she would see what she could do.. so i still have hopes of at least one day... *prays*.. oh that the only other bad thing.. I don;t get to go to church ><.. but oh well God understands ^-^...

New things.. well not much... i'm im process of getting a new cellphone.. and it'll be, as I like to call it "discustingly cute"... yup it's gonna be a PINK cellphone.. it can't get any cuter... but I still think it's worth it it has fairly good fuctions.. Just need to wait for it to arrive T^T...

ooops.. got scolded for posting on lj in work hours ... *runs*

Bonjour tout le monde..!!

News about me ^_^, for those interested..  Well everything is fine now.. after a week of exams and presentations.. (and a weekend of partying and visits ;;>.>) I survived and hopefully with decent marks.. (or so i believe)..

Finally my stay in Tours is coming to and end.. and i couldn't be happier... =p Tours is a nice place.. but it's too much of a small town for me.. i need 24h internet NOW... so behind in my anime/manga/dramas T^T (minus LoveCom, RomeoxJuliet, TRC and ProDai <3) Plus leaving Tours = classes are over!! I'm almost graduated !!!

Tomorrow we are leaving for Paris finally!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! I wanna see Paris soooo sooo soooo much.... and after Rome <3 ( and Mum <3).. I'm exited!! classes are over and only one hw due woohoo!!!.. only scary thing.. LUGGAGE.. tihs! ! so much stuff i have no idea where i'm gonna put all that stuff.. and i even threw out some stuff already.. not to mention.. still food in my fridge.. =___= 

pictures of castles.. later ;;>.> *runs and  hides*

hehehehe

hello my dear friends LONG TIME  no see ><... I have to excuse myself for not posting/answering or showing any kind of living signs lately... to be honest lots of classes and excursions.. no time even to post pics other that the ones others have posted of me in facebook ..  at least our stay in Tours is close to an ending.. though i did enjoy it.. it's time to leave.. we part Friday 22nd.. so a week from tomorrow!! to Paris for a week.. and then 5 days in Rome <3 and it'll be over.. T^T

I miss you all so much T^T .. I miss Venezuela as always.. and for the first time in my life I miss Vancouver/Burnaby... SO much... I miss my house and my room.. and even my clothes !!! and i miss food!!!!!!! I WANT STEAK!!! so much ... it's not even funny.. (sorry for vegetarians)...

and last thing tomorrow in my b-day.. (leaving for Nantes with Wendy and Ksenia for 2 days.. )

My love to everyone.. pictures.. maybe from Paris (hotel with internet  woohoo) if not.. from Vancouver.. =p...

I'm here <3
 YEY I got here alive.. thanks that i met  with the whole group in the airport xp...

I'll post next week with more details.. no time today cause librari closes at 12 and typing with a keybord where the a's are at the q's place the w instead of z and , intead of m's is not easy DX.... later my loves <3 <3 <3

yey another wallpaper attempt.. this actually is version #2 of it.. (v1 was kinda simple).. Again I chose Tsubasa: Reservoir Chronicles.. cause I just love it <3 and I totally adored this pic xDD... hope someone likes it ^^;;Type your cut contents here.

sorry for the small version >< but when i up it on Imageshack it shrank .. oh well it i ever get it uploaded somewhere  I'll let you know..
so what do you all think? .. Are my attempts going anywhere?

Hello Everyone how have you all been? hope that well and that exams didn't treat you so bad.. 

As for me.. well i was done a little while ago.. for the past.. 2 weeks I've been doing very little ^^;; buying stuff i needed for my trip and stuff.. I can;t believe I'm leaving in a week!!... eeepp.. I'm exited ... and scared Dx.. but it can't be helped.. it would be worst if i was not scared xp.. I'm gonna be so far away >.<;; and not much Internet access *dies* ;;>.> 8 weeks without anime/drama/manga updates will be bad.. even when I go to Vzla I manage to dl some of it ;;>.>.. oh well.. I'll make a way +___+.. on the other hand I dl like 4 series to watch there ^^;;

The trip sound like more fun everyday.. though I'm a bit worried.. because it seems will do lots of exercise.. er.. running.. walking.. <strike> biking </strike> falling.. (yup I don't know how to ride a bike).. ~___~ I guess I'll have to get used to it.... it's healthy.. I guess.. I hope I'll try lots of yummy food too xD <33 and meet new ppl ^^ .. and get good grades ;;>.>.. gambarimasho!!

Later my dears ^_~ I hope life treat you all very well in the future... I'll try update before I leave ^-^ 

*huggles of doOooom for everyone <3*

yup new Lj Look <33333333333333333 this one I'll keep until I come back from the fieldschool XD (leaving in around 2 weeks<) i just luff it <33 Beauty pop is one of my fav mangas.. I had been thinking about making a BP background for such a long time!! but considering i only have scans of the manga covers .. well there was not a lot of choice.. xp I still like the final result.. though the full body pics the have weird expressions.. the closeups are way nicer <3...

Now that I'm talking about this ... when i was making this look i realized smth.. I always use very similar colors O.o.. last look (TRC) was the same yellow/turquoise/bright pink/green/red.. now is the same minus the red.. and i used to have one with same colors +electric blue/purple for Ouran... the weirdest thing is i don't really like bright colors ;;>.>.. maybe I'm just going insane..... 

~_______~ time to get of the computer so much PS is killing my eyes.. / head x.X

Laters <33

how is everyone??.. hope that well and that exams are not killing you too much ^^;;;

It's a busy time, nee? same goes for me as you can imagine ~_~.. but at least i'll be done by next saturday.. yey.. and oh noes.. it means i should be studying now ;;>.> (or writing final papers ;;>.>)

What have  I been up  too lately?.. not much.. school: essays,exams,classes,presentation.. fieldschool preparations: buy stuff, pack stuff.... anime/manga/dramas.. and that's about it ^^;;

I haven;t updated in a long while.. because.. there's not much to talk about =p.. my family is well thanks God.. =3 getting ready to move in October ~_~.. right now my parents bro and sis are in Easter holidays traveling .. and my older bro and sis in law.. well here at home.. The family upstairs is fine too ^^ grandma came back today.. and i went to the movies with *makes up nickname for little neighbor* Vie-chan xD.. We went see blades of glory with her friends.. ^^;; it's funny how I look like one of them.. (minus the fact i'm not asian ^^;;).. they are all so nice ^^ it was fun .. even though the movie was not one i would choose.. it was fun.. it was really funny XP

Things to do for next week.. Final paper for french.. about a play.. final paper for English.. about poetry DX modern one...and 2 French finals .. yippei ;_;... oh well it could be worst...
after that get ready for the trip >< so many things that still need to be done ><.. 

about anime, drama and manga.. lots lately... anime: dgm, death note, yamato nadeshiko shishi hegen, detective loki ragnarok,and smth else.. i also finished Saiunkoku Monogatari (with depressed me cause i didn;t know it was the last ep T^T and i really liked it..) School rumble 2nd season xD omg.. SR is soo funny ... and Ashita no Nadja... !_! oh and i watched the raw of ep 1 of Kamichama Karin xD ... Manga.. just updates..TRC is getting soo awesome O_O!! it's becoming kinda more like X/1999.. the plot is coming together.. and some questions are being solved.. sadly one chapter a week is not enough T^T... Dramas.. well most of them finished >< Goong S.. had a pretty ending xD.. HYD2 too.. but it was funnier <333 so fun they should make HYD3 !!!.. i watched Reaching for the stars.. meehh it was ok.. the rest are a bit stuck because it;s finals time for lots of ppl xp oh well i understand them =3

so.. not much to say other than that for now.. i wish you all good luck in your finals !!! and in everything else.. ^_~ hopefully next time will come sooner and hopefully I'll have and updated look for lj <3 (I'm thinking Beauty Pop for next look *_______*)

meh =_= I'm back at procrastinating it's not even funny.. and the essay i have to do was due on tuesday.. >< I really should get something done soon >.< before 11:30 am today if possible ... though i'm my defense i got sick .. or at least i made myself sick on Tuesday >.< ...

other than that not much .. busy with uni.. and getting ready for my trip @_@.. it's amazing all the things one has to get done before traveling >.<.. plus the semester will end soon >________< more reason to get stuff done!! so busy.. no time for walls, icons or fun. ;_; To finish my semester I have that essay due.. a composition for french class, a creative project DX (which i have no idea what to do ) *not creative* <--just sad, another literary analysis for french, a term paper and 2 french finals all in the next 3 weeks ~_~ God save me.. and my grades..

Thinking of this as my last semester is really not helping me =________= my will has gone from 0.33 to -20... even when i like the readings writting essays about them is a torture... T^T aye my love for education where hath thou gone?

Other than that .. err... *nothing to say really* oh yeah! i got a facebook account lol but under an alias.. i dun really like to go leaving my name/pictures over the Internet *paranoid as always*

so this was for you another pointless post by moi ;p

Au revoir~

..oh well i decided to put aside attempts # 1 and 2 for a while ~_~ cause i think i need more lite with them and i dun feel like starting them over lately.. soo i decided to make a Nodame Cantabile one <3 .. actually this is my second NC one but the first one is not nearly finished =p.. this one i really like.. but it has smth I need to fix and i dun know how >.<;;;

oh well here it is...

hehehe *cough cough* I mean it's done .. my new lj look <3333 i luff it it looks kinda crazy and way too colorful ^^;;. but i still like it it took forever to make so I'm happy with the result... i kinda dislike that i had to squish everything together ^^;; the wallpaper size looked better to me =/

So why did i take so long making that.. first... i changed the colors of part of the clothes the guys were wearing.. and after i made backgrounds for every pic ^^;;; yup i do things taking the long way... and after i made the general background.. (;;>.> yeah i know it's crooked in some parts ;;>.> but i did my best) after that i put small pics on the background and added the text <333

 I used the 2 last color pages that have been out on Tsubasa <333 yup i' obsessed.. and i finally learnt to use photoshop.. or some of it at least ^__^;;

~_~ wah i said i was going to post on Friday but i was too lazy to.. I'm still working on my new lj background.. <3333 i can't wait till it's done I think it'll look good.. or at least I hope so because it's taking me sooooooooooo long to finish it ;_; .. i finally got photoshot yey!!.. but i dun quite know how to use it lol.. so for  background  I'm still working with paint ^^;; and the program that came with scanner i hope that's good enough

other than that not much to say.. i'm kinda tired right now ~_~ and i have class tomorrow T^T.. at least it's only one *parties*..

laters.. hopefully next time i'll have a new look on ly lj <33333333333333333333333 (sadly it's not Kobato >.<.. oh well Tsubasa is awesome too <3333333)

>.< wahh i'm moody right now... ok I'm just hungry.. but that's what makes me moody faster... how has been my life?.. busy >.<.. uni is going crazy.. and i had soooooo much to read.. plus I have to write some stuff for next week =__= at least I  did most of my reading that i need for now... i think.. i hope.. but i'm doing NOTHING else today... other than dinner ;;>.>       and maybe some icons <3

I sooo want to change my layout for lj... hana kimi is awesome.. but i was something more.. clamp? xD;; i also need more icons<33 i still need to but my neigbour for photoshop though... =/ but i can do that today

=/ i'll come update later today hopefully maybe i'll have a layout to boast about then xp...  now! home or somewhere to eat ~__~

wahh ..I haven't come to complain about my life post lately... .. why? school is being evil to me.. even at this moment I have bunch of things to do.. but i can't manage to focus on any of them >.< *stabs books* (<-- not really helpful)

Last week was insane 3 essays + midterm.. this week.. better.. but not great.. 1 midterm + Mansfield park (long novel) +response +unexpected French novel to read @_@... i wanna sleep for the whole weekend =______=... At least good things happened this week <333 I got in the France fieldschool program, it was not supposed to be hard.. but it's nice to know for sure <333 yey.. finally the fact that I'm going to France *crosses fingers/looks up* is sinking in my brain *_______* can't wait!! yet I'm scared ;_;... makes no sense considering i already live away from most my family.. including my parents.. and i do mostly everything by myself.. yet... it's sooooooooooooo scary >.<;;;;;.. Also.. got some money from bursaries <333333333 yey.. I can't believe i learnt about this just recently >.< my parents could have saved so much money ;_; *hits head.. baka!* .. oh well.. better late than never..

About anime/manga/drama... not much.. keeping up with updates of everything is enough to make me waste all my time and not study.. >.< I really should stop watching/reading some stuff.. some are not that good ... yet i dun wanna >.<;;; *runs like little kid*... nvm that ^^;;;...

Ok time to do my HW!! YOSH!! *ties white headband and goes sit staring at her books*

heheh test about .. eto ME! ^^;; *hides under rock* everyone try it please <333333 you might get to know smth new about me ... heheh.. yey, I stopped procrastinating smth lol..

Create your own Friend Test here

yey happy V-day everyone.. I made a card.. i did my best so that it didn't end up too crappy... but it did anyways.. anyways feelings is what counts =p ... <33333333333333


*huggles everyone* <333333

since saturday i'vebeen eating lots of fortune cookies.. XD they are awesome.. xDDDDDD sweet and fortune!.. ok i dun quite belive in fortunes but it's kinda fun one in a while.. i'm kinda surprise that out of all the ones i've eaten so far none have contradicted themselves.. (thou most didn;t come true XD) though the one i ate this morning might have been right... it said smth about smth unexpected happening well 2 unexpected things happened... one.. i wen to class after finishing my essay in record time of 2h and 30m (1500).. you can imagine how good it is not.. xp.. and ZOMG there was no class the prof is sick Dx i feel bad for him.. and unlike i always do i never wished anyone to get sick this time for me to have time to do better on my essay...and the second  thing.. i saw one friend from uni today.. one i hadn't seen since i went back to Vzla last summer... and now i know why... she has a Baby O_O;;; she is my age is if i'm not mistaken.. the baby is around one month ( didn;t have time to ask ><) and soooo cute .. dammit i want a baby !! not to have one *goes poke her siblings: get me a nephew/niece!!* i even met the dad.. sadly it was really fast no chance to talk ><.. wow.. i can believe that only after one year she is already married and with a baby .. and she look a bit dif too.. and to think i've been looking the same and acting the same since i'm 15 ... ^^;;;;

oh well... time to take a nap before i start my essay for tomorrow and dinner ~_~

I always thought leaving an essay for the last minute felt bad.. and having a word count of 5 at 12am was stressing.... til today.. when i have 2 essays do and same word count... gosh i really must be dumb .. nee?

 Procrastination is not the way to go.. but is the path i chose. =_______=.. i seriously need some one to hit me with a harisen every time i get distracted ;;>.>  that might work... or not..

Other than that.. well the week was the same.. long school was boring... Saturday on the other hand was uber fun <3333333333. I went to Richmond and met with Rukia =3 we had lunch in Chinese place.. and turns out I know how to hold chopsticks the right way yey xDD.. the food was yummy <333 after that we went to different places/stores.. i ended up buying lots of food i had never tried including manju and onigiris XDDD all yummy... ( minus the sushi ^^;;;;.. dun hate me sushi lovers) I seriously ate too much that day xp but it was all good and really fun.. plus i've never been in those places so it was a bit of tourism for me heheheh.. Sunday was ok.. churh early in the morning and after LOTS of drama .. yup the current source of all my problems.. seriously i'll stop buying cds.. that might stop my dls for a while i hope DX

So the drama list grows.. currently added Lunch Queen and Nodame Canatibile both are great but Nodame is completely hilarious xDDDDDDDDDDDD i just love it.. specially  the violent/anime-manga scenes lol they   kill me .. plus main character are awesome.. girl, Nodame, is funny, such a pig too lol.. butshe reminds me of L.. or maybe N.. + any shoujo manga female lead XD... and the guy, Chiaki, i keep thinking of him as Light+Rui+Taro XDD plus the music is so pretty .. <3 awesome drama and so addictive T^T.. odd i dl it with french subs XD;;; now i can say I read some french in the weekend ...

T^T .. *goes back to staring at her blank word document  her TWO blank word documents...*

~________~ it seem like i like to feel the pressure of writing 500 in 20 min DX.... current situation 1 h to class.. and i need eat lunch >.<;;; and write a one page (single space) response to disappearing Moon Cafe novel.. ~___~ i started yesterday.. but i was sleepy cause it was kinda late and i couldn't come up witha good theme Dx (i forgot i even had to do it so i started even later than usual....)

French 301 went ok.. better than other days ... not great yet.. I'm so scared about next week's exam.. ;_;...

Next week I'll be so busy with school T^T .. 3 essays due plus midterm .. Dx.. and i wanted to buy cheap chocolate after valentine's .. nooooo my chocohappiness.... gone....

about other things.. my other classes are going ok.. french 230 is nice.. ^__^ slow and interesting.. and i'm actually learning to analyze poetry ... *and yeah i'm supposed to know that already considering i'm 4th year english major.. but i dun quite...* my 327 engl is good too ^__^ prof is nice.. class is ok.. confusing at times.. but the real reason i like it so much.. i got an A - .. yey... i dun get many "A"s.. and i was expecting prf to call me to his office to talk about my essay... cause that always happens after i hand in my first essay ;;>.>.... 

Anime/drama/manga side... animes.. same.. lately some updates on Saiunkoku <3.. but others are pretty much the same.. dgm.. fillers ep are the worst DX... and DN.. i dl last ep in spanich lol cause it was translated faster... odd... I think I'll start dl Angelic Layer ^^... manga... updates of my new mangas as always <3 TRC is getting sooo good.. not to mention Kobato and xxxHolic.. oh and i bought vol 8 of Ouran <3... i started dl complex  (shoujo) too.. weird funny manga.. =3.. and  last dramas.. eto.. i re watched Kimi wa petto <3, watched some Goong S with right timing xp.... hana kimi is kinda stuck >.<.. HYD2 .. i dl ep 5 yesterday.. but haven't watched it yet >.<;;; and i started dl  lunch queen (j) and the first ep of corner with love (TW)... .. 

O__________O time to write/run.. expect lots of typos ^^;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
